<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>There were many problems still left.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402000' id='t-402000'>And they're still with us, and you haven't solved them,</span>
