<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='914000' id='t-914000'>We have families that self-destruct,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='917000' id='t-917000'>friends that betray us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='919000' id='t-919000'>Unbearable psychological pressures bear down on us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922000' id='t-922000'>I've never met a person in the world</span>
