<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1519000' id='t-1519000'>and changed my life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1521000' id='t-1521000'>And now I'm ready,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1524000' id='t-1524000'>when I hear that call,</span>
